title: N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 10 §§ 14-5.116 - Cleaning record
content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 10 §§ 14-5.116 - Cleaning record

State Regulations
A record of cleaning operations is to be maintained by the operator. It is to be located in each machine or be returned daily to headquarters, and is to be available at the time of inspection and be current for at least the past 30 days. Notes
